cs.FL, cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.CC, cs.IT

Reasoning: 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with infinite words and their complexity measured with respect to finite automata. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is also likely as the paper explores logical characterizations of the different classifications of infinite words. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper discusses the hierarchy over infinite words and explores connections between different classes. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is another possibility as the paper measures the complexity of infinite words with respect to different classes of objects. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper deals with measuring the complexity of infinite words.
